### Variables
@baseUrl = http://localhost:8000/api/v1
@contentType = application/json
@appId = 01KP9SB2XTGF0GKJ7ZA9D0DYXR

### Create Application - Web API
POST {{baseUrl}}/applications
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "name": "web-api",
  "description": "Main REST API service for customer-facing web application"
}

### Create Application - Mobile App
POST {{baseUrl}}/applications
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "name": "mobile-app",
  "description": "iOS and Android mobile application backend"
}

### Create Application - Batch Processor
POST {{baseUrl}}/applications
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "name": "batch-processor",
  "description": "Nightly batch job processor for data aggregation"
}

### Get All Applications
GET {{baseUrl}}/applications

### Get Application by ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/applications/{{appId}}

### Delete Application (cascades to its configuration)
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/applications/{{appId}}
